		<ul>
			<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.info.uni-karlsruhe.de/software/ycomp">yComp</a> - <i>visualization for program graphs</i></li>
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li> Frontends
		<ul>
			<li> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/cparser/">CParser</a> - C-Frontend</li>
			<li> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://github.com/MatzeB/bytecode2firm">bytecode2firm</a> - Javabytecode frontend</li>
			<li> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://github.com/MatzeB/fluffy">Fluffy Language</a></li>
